          "process_md": "&amp;gt; **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the official website of Swachh Bharat Mission (Grameen) at [https://swachhbharatmission.ddws.gov.in/](https://swachhbharatmission.ddws.gov.in/)\n**Step 2:** On the home page, click on ‘Application Form for IHHL’ under the Citizen Corner section.\n**Step 3**: If you are not already registered, click on ‘[Citizen Registration](https://sbm.gov.in/SBM_DBT/Secure/DBT/DBT_Registration.aspx)’. Enter your mobile number and verify it using the OTP received.\n**Step 4:** After verifying your mobile number, enter your name, gender, address, state name, and the Captcha code. Then, click on the ‘Submit’ button.\n**Step 5:** A successful registration message will appear on the screen after submitting the details.\n&amp;gt; **Login to Apply under the Scheme:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the official website of Swachh Bharat Mission (Grameen) again at [https://swachhbharatmission.ddws.gov.in/](https://swachhbharatmission.ddws.gov.in/)\n**Step 2:** On the home page, click on ‘Application Form for IHHL’ under the Citizen Corner section.\n**Step 3:** Enter your registered mobile number, the received OTP, and the Security Code, then click on ‘[Sign-In](https://sbm.gov.in/sbm_dbt/secure/login.aspx)’.\n**Step 4:** After successfully signing in, click on ‘New Application’ under the ‘Modules’ section located on the left corner of the screen.\n**Step 5:** Complete the application form, upload the required documents, and click on the ‘Apply’ button.\n"
        },
